[normal]Written evidence submitted by the [bold]All Party Parliamentary Group on Population, Development and Reproductive Health, and Marie [bold]Stopes[bold] International[bold]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
